model.name: Damier Denim Trucker Jacket
model.disambiguatingDescription: This graphic piece plays the capsule's reengineered Damier motif on a classic denim shape. Inspired by a 1914 greetings card, the iconic pattern incorporates pen strokes and a "Marque Louis Vuitton déposée" signature. Crafted in a regular fit from cotton fabric, it features Egret metallic hardware.

additionalProperty.name: detailedDescription
additionalProperty.value:
• 98% Cotton, 2% Elastane
  • Ocean
  • Regular Fit
  • Model wears a FR 50 size
  • Model measurements : chest 32’’ / 81 cm, height 6'2’’ / 188 cm
  • Made in France
